    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so if we're talking about the actual \"look\" or \"vibe\" of a global professional, what are the specific standards for things like dress code and dining? like, if a client wants to ensure they look like they belong in any top-tier boardroom or gala, what's the gold standard they should follow?",
