      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For the gold standard, lean into timeless, impeccably tailored classics; think muted, luxurious fabrics and perfectly fitted silhouettes that transcend fleeting trends. In formal settings, conservative elegance is key—a well-cut suit or sophisticated evening wear speaks louder than any loud fashion statement. When dining, observe the host's lead, practice refined table manners without ostentation, and never rush the experience to project calm, confident control.",
